<H3> <TI>   Tian Jiyun Attends Inauguration of Sino-ROK Venture </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2803142594 Beijing XINHUA in English 1408 GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2803142594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


