<F P=100> Northeast Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Asia Development Bank Inspects Heilongjiang Highway Project </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0603071194 Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 5 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0603071194 </F>
<F P=104>  Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A six-member group from the Asia Development Bank 
arrived in Harbin on the evening of 4 March on their mission of 
carrying out a six-day on-the-spot examination of the project of 
building the highway section between Harbin and Jiamusi on the 
designed highway between Tongjiang and (Shanya), which will be 
built with the loan offered by the Asia Development Bank. The 
section of Tongjiang-(Shanya) highway in the province is 641 km 
long. The highway section between Harbin and Jiamusi, which was 
designed in the first-phase project, is 332 km long. The total 
investment made in the highway project is 2.2 billion yuan 
renminbi. The loan offered by the Asia Development Bank is $140 
million. The State Council has formally approved the loan for 
the highway project. 

</TEXT>

