<H3> <TI>   Liaoning Secretary Addresses Standing Committee Meeting </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2603084094 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 25 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2603084094 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Today the provincial party committee held an 
enlarged standing committee meeting. Gu Jinchi and other 
provincial leaders who had attended the Second Session of the 
Eighth National People's Congress [NPC] and the Second Session 
of the Eighth National Committee of the Chinese People's 
Political Consultative Conference [CPPCC] relayed the guidelines 
of these two sessions. 
  At the meeting, Chen Suzhi, vice chairman of the provincial 
people's congress standing committee, relayed the speeches given 
by Comrade Jiang Zemin at the meeting of party leaders and at a 
meeting with the Liaoning delegation during the second session 
of the eighth NPC. Lin Sheng, vice chairman of the provincial 
people's congress standing committee, relayed the guidelines of 
the Second Session of the Eighth National CPPCC Committee. 
Zhang Guoguang, deputy secretary of the provincial party 
committee, relayed the speeches given by Comrades Jiang Zemin, 
Li Peng, and Zhu Rongji at the national rural work conference. 
  Gu Jinchi, secretary of the provincial party committee, 
worked out plans for several major tasks to be carried out in 
the province this year. He pointed out: It is necessary to act 
in line with the central spirit of seizing the opportunity, 
deepening reform, expanding opening up, promoting development, 
and maintaining stability, properly handle the relations of 
reform, development, and stability, and under the situation of 
maintaining social stability, guarantee the smooth 
implementation of the reform plans. At present, we should 
attend to agricultural production, seize the opportune moment 
for spring plowing, and guarantee the farming acreage, 
particularly the farming acreage of wheat. He stressed: We 
should realistically organize and guide industrial production 
and end the downward situation in industry. 
  At the end of his speech, Gu Jinchi called on leaders at all 
levels to improve work style, go deeply to the grass roots, 
strengthen grass-roots organizational construction, and do some 
practical things for the grass roots. 

</TEXT>

